Yahoo! Inc. Preparing Layoffs, Could Affect Thousands-Reuters
Monday, 5 Mar 2012 12:11pm EST
Reuters reported that according to a technology blog, Yahoo! Inc.'s new chief executive is preparing a significant restructuring of the Company, including layoffs that could cut thousands of employees from its payroll. The moves could be announced as soon as the end of the month and would represent the first major changes under CEO Scott Thompson. The changes will focus on its products group, as well as on research, marketing and public relations and businesses that are not core to the Company, according to the report on March 5, 2012, in the blog AllThingsDigital.com, which cited anonymous sources.Â 
